Package model.entity

Class Notification

java.lang.Object
model.entity.Notification
@Entity public class Notification extends Object
Represents a notification entity in the system. Each notification is associated with a user and may be linked to a reservation. It contains messages in multiple languages and a timestamp for when it was created.
